{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "During that time, my father wanted to spare us the humiliation of-- of being taken out during the night into the-- into the square.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we built-- we had-- in our-- in our building, there was a small basement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my father had managed to-- to find old wood and cover the floor of the-- of the basement where the-- where the door used to be.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So when you walked into-- to the-- to the the room, you couldn't-- you weren't aware that it was a basement underneath.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from the wall in the kitchen, we were able to lift up two planks of wood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we used to be able to slide in into the basement from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So every time when-- when they used to start knocking on the windows and chasing the entire ghetto into-- into the square, we used to slide in into the basement.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we would sit there for an hour or two, as long as it took.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were spared the humiliation of being taken out int-- in-- into the-- into the square.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the-- my father did it by himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I was aware that they're doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall-- I don't think I was-- I did much to help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he built it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was other people in that house that were liv-- there was also another photographer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this man, together with my mother, ran-- ran the business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they were also included into this hiding place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- I think that this gentleman helped my father to-- to build it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So every time when this used to happen, we used to slide in into the basement and wait out till we heard the noise of the people returning.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
